Jazsmin Lewis https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jazsmin_Lewis 0 Jazsmin Lewis-Kelley (born March 22, 1976) is an American actress. She is best known for her starring role as the title character in the 2005 film Traci Townsend and as Calvin's pregnant wife Jennifer Palmer in the Barbershop film series.
